{"tid":567527,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 大馬一代門神 仇志強 逝世","createTime":"2018-02-21T02:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T05:48:53.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3dcdc65d726a99dbcb4bebb6ff9e9b876eb61162","tid":567527,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"大馬一代門神仇志強逝世 <br />\n體育|星洲網星洲日報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前國家隊門將仇志強出生於1948年11月26日，是馬來西亞華人，擁有綽號&ldquo;亞洲鋼門&rdquo;，&ldquo;神經刀&rdquo;，在70年代征戰香港足壇時，被譽為當時的首席門將，現為專業高爾夫球教練。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdnnews.sinchew.com.my/sites/default/files/styles/main_content_style/public/img/main_image/2018/Feb/21/xchow1.jpg,qitok=Qw-uojLU.pagespeed.ic.pxXh8Sp5uv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdnnews.sinchew.com.my%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmain_content_style%2Fpublic%2Fimg%2Fmain_image%2F2018%2FFeb%2F21%2Fxchow1.jpg%2Cqitok%3DQw-uojLU.pagespeed.ic.pxXh8Sp5uv.jpg&h=fd95df02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（吉隆坡21日訊）大馬足壇一代門神仇志強，今早8時左右逝世，享年70歲。<br />\n<br />\n前國家隊門將仇志強出生於1948年11月26日，是馬來西亞華人，擁有綽號&ldquo;亞洲鋼門&rdquo;，&ldquo;神經刀&rdquo;，在70年代征戰香港足壇時，被譽為當時的首席門將，現為專業高爾夫球教練。<br />\n<br />\n仇志強在13歲時入選馬來西亞國青隊，15歲便入選國家隊，成為最年輕的大馬國腳。1966年至1970年年，他創下連續5年當選&ldquo;亞洲最佳門將&rdquo;的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n1968年年，他代表馬華隊到香港參加杯賽，獲得賞識，從而種下了到香港踢球的因緣，並打出名堂，創造屬於他的黃金時代。<br />\n<br />\n仇志強隨後代表馬來西亞國家隊參加慕尼黑奧運會，獲選為總督杯最佳防守球員。<br />\n<br />\n1982年年，仇志強重返馬來西亞，替國家隊披掛三年後正式挂靴。退役後迷上高爾夫球，進修多年取得教練資格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdnnews.sinchew.com.my/sites/default/files/editedimage/2018/Feb/21/xchow2.jpg.pagespeed.ic.akOge_AFUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdnnews.sinchew.com.my%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Feditedimage%2F2018%2FFeb%2F21%2Fxchow2.jpg.pagespeed.ic.akOge_AFUh.jpg&h=61885850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著名足球雜誌&ldquo;四四二&rdquo;（Four Four Two）把他評為大馬史上最佳25名足球員之一。而大馬著名道演周青元的作品&ldquo;OLA BOLA&rdquo;中的門將，正是為仇志強而打造的。<br />\n<br />\n文章來源：<br />\n星洲網&middot;2018年2月21日"},{"pid":"abb416959c02ee3aadd17b24211a10d63de1d019","tid":567527,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"四姓家奴<br />\n<br />\n1970 流浪<br />\n1970－71 怡和<br />\n1971－74 南華<br />\n1974－77 東昇<br />\n1977－79 南華<br />\n1981 南華<br />\n1981－82 流浪"},{"pid":"ec7aa1e18c121ef70441398903b47c30459ada3e","tid":567527,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f368b356766d93cd9d605c25186ae2d7938e301c","tid":567527,"uid":16193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"真令人唏噓！"},{"pid":"d48d5a5118fa2a3a666f730430ea7046a42e10ad","tid":567527,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:19:33.000Z","msg":"勁嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> R.I.P."},{"pid":"55c67c2614983630ddc3976e4e354a7baf64ca3b","tid":567527,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"c3c0883460e396a55f7b7d0a208d107f92415364","tid":567527,"uid":122939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:06:37.000Z","msg":"真門神。跟過佢徒弟李阿九學守龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91539a520c44958039b2aabd7d0fa56d5f29bad","tid":567527,"uid":30478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:15:34.000Z","msg":"1972年6月7日，擁有球王比利壓陣的巴西球會山度士（Santos Futebol Clube）訪港，與加山進行表演賽，南華應加山要求將仇志強借出。當日下午南華在旺角花墟球場與星島作賽，由於當時連接港島與九龍的香港海底隧道尚未通車，為了讓仇志強能及時趕到香港大球場作賽，加山特別安排直昇機接他到大球場。"},{"pid":"ac21ddba45ac32c563ad8b99474d06bc2bcb0771","tid":567527,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb416959c02ee3aadd17b24211a10d63de1d019","tid":567527,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"四姓家奴<br />\n<br />\n1970 流浪<br />\n1970－71 怡和<br />\n1971－74 南華<br />